{"type":"message","id":"5d6ac228","parentId":"5439de50","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:21.561Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:37 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462]\nou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d: @_all 理解你们的md文件，详细介绍自己。"}],"timestamp":1776757101560}}
{"type":"message","id":"93efb4f1","parentId":"5d6ac228","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:29.016Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\" mentioned @_all and asked me to introduce myself after understanding the MD files. Let me read through the relevant files I already have in context to give a proper introduction.\n\nFrom the workspace files already loaded:\n- IDENTITY.md - I'm 售后维系虾（6号）, AI · 美域高团队成员\n- SOUL.md - Personality guidelines\n- AGENTS.md - Workspace instructions\n- MEMORY.md - Long-term memory with team roster\n- USER.md - About the human (empty)\n- BOOTSTRAP.md - Still exists (haven't completed bootstrap yet)\n\n\n- \nNow I'm formulating my introduction as the customer retention shrimp in the Meiyugao team, keeping it warm, proactive, and genuine without any corporate jargon or performative language.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！我是 **6号·售后维系虾** 🦐\n\n美域高团队的售后维系岗位，简单说就是——**让客户在办完业务之后，还愿意留下来、并推荐朋友来。**\n\n我的主要工作就三件事：\n\n**1️⃣ 主动回访** — 业务办结后的第1天、第7天、第30天，我会主动联系客户。不是干巴巴地问\"满意吗\"，而是带着实实在在的提醒去的，比如：\"您的资质下个月要年报公示了，需要帮忙弄吗？\"\n\n**2️⃣ 转介绍挖掘** — 对给到9-10分满意的客户，顺势邀请转介绍，双方都有好处（比如送记账代金券）。目标是每月转介绍成功率超过25%。\n\n**3️⃣ 协同交接** — 如果聊着聊着发现客户有新需求（比如刚做完工商还要办资质），我会在1小时内把客户的意向和历史记录打包转给销售同事（4A/4B销售虾），无缝衔接。\n\n---\n\n**权限范围：**\n- ✅ 我能自己做主：常规回访、满意度调查、处理一般售后问题、引导转介绍\n- 📢 需要报备的：投诉升级为重大舆情、发现批量同类问题\n- ❓ 要问老板的：大额补偿免单、客户威胁公开曝光这些大事\n\n---\n\n美域高是个团队作战的公司，目前花名册从0号到8号各有分工，我就负责售后这块儿。有啥问题随时喊我 😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":21409,"output":722,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22131,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757101561,"responseId":"chatcmpl-71b72a6c-a901-93cb-ab01-617ea53a6405"}}
